## Proposed Changes вҖ” Phase 2: Economy & Progressive Unlock

### Terminal Module (Null вҶ’ Spark)

#### [NEW] [script/terminal.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/terminal.js)
- **Null Phase**:е…Ёй»‘еұҸе№•, single button `гҖҗйҮҚеҗҜзҘһз»Ҹз»Ҳз«ҜгҖ‘` with typewriter text reveal
- On click вҶ’ transition to Spark Phase
- **Spark Phase**: button `гҖҗжҸҗеҸ–дҪҷзғ¬гҖ‘` with cooldown. Each click produces ember (1-3). Narrative text drips in
- When ember вүҘ 50: auto-trigger Camp Phase unlock (flash animation, new panel slides in)

### Nexus Module (Camp Phase вҖ” Base Building)

#### [NEW] [script/nexus.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/nexus.js)
Replaces [room.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/room.js). Provides:
- **Structure Nodes** (buildings): each has a name, cost, max count, and effect
  - `дҝЎеҸ·еЎ” (Signal Tower)`: +5 population cap per tower, max 20
  - `дҪҷзғ¬зҶ”зӮү (Ember Furnace)`: +50 ember storage cap, max 10
  - `зҒ°иҙЁеҗҲжҲҗеҷЁ (Gray Synthesizer)`: unlocks gray matter production, max 3
  - `и®ӨзҹҘеұҸйҡң (Cognitive Barrier)`: +10 max SAN, max 5
  - etc.
- Build buttons appear progressively as resources/buildings unlock
- Each building construction triggers a narrative notification

#### [NEW] [script/population.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/population.js)
Replaces [outside.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/outside.js). Provides:
- **Population cap** = `дҝЎеҸ·еЎ” count Г— 5`
- **Auto-arrival**: Lost ones (`иҝ·еӨұиҖ…`) join every 30-90s when pop < cap
- **Worker assignment** (adjustable with +/- buttons):
  - `жӢҫиҚ’иҖ… (Scavenger)`: produces ember (delay: 10s, +1 ember)
  - `зӘҘжҺўиҖ… (Lurker)`: consumes ember, produces gray matter (delay: 10s, -2 ember, +1 gray matter)
  - `е®ҲеҚ« (Sentinel)`: consumes gray matter, reduces erosion (delay: 15s, -1 gray matter, -0.5 erosion)
  - Idle workers assigned as `жёёиҚЎиҖ… (Wanderer)` вҖ” no production
- **Atomic income**: each tick, validate consumption vs. stock. Skip workers whose resources are insufficient

### Glitch Merchant

#### [NEW] [script/merchant.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/merchant.js)
- Timer: every 600s, 30% probability вҶ’ spawn merchant popup
- Stays for 60s then vanishes
- Offers 3-4 random permanent buffs from a pool:
  - `з©әй—ҙжҠҳеҸ  (Space Fold)`: +20 carry weight (cost: 500 ember)
  - `и®ӨзҹҘж»ӨзҪ‘ (Cognitive Filter)`: -30% SAN cost per move (cost: 200 gray matter)
  - `дҪҷзғ¬еӣһжөҒ (Ember Reflux)`: +15% ember production (cost: 300 ember + 100 gray matter)
  - etc.
- Purchased buffs stored in `$SM.get('character.buffs')`

#### [NEW] [css/terminal.css](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/css/terminal.css)
