## Proposed Changes вҖ” Phase 4: Map & Survival (Leap Phase)

#### [NEW] [script/rift_map.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/rift_map.js)
Replaces [world.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/world.js):
- **Sparse matrix**: only visited/adjacent tiles stored, infinite potential space
- **Viewport**: 21Г—21 grid rendered around player, fog-of-war for unvisited
- **Controls**: WASD keyboard + tap-to-move on adjacent cells (mobile)
- **Tile types**: void, debris, ruin, anomaly, cache, exit
- **Rift coordinate synthesis**: spend Whispers to unlock new map regions
- **UI reveal**: first coordinate synthesized вҶ’ right panel violently tears open (CSS animation)

#### [NEW] [script/survival.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/survival.js)
- **Supply axis**: movement costs `й«ҳиғҪжө“зј©ж¶І (Concentrate)`. If depleted вҶ’ each move costs HP & SAN directly
- **Weight axis**: fixed carry limit (base 30, upgradeable). Loot has weight. Over-weight вҶ’ must drop items
- **Death**: lose all backpack items, respawn at camp with narrative text

#### [NEW] [script/combat.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/combat.js)
Replaces combat in [events.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/events.js):
- **ATB (Active Time Battle)**: action bar fills over time, attack when full
- **God-Pressure scaling**: enemies gain `+godPressure%` to stats
- **Button feedback**: CSS `.combat-shake` on hit, `.combat-depress` on click
- Weapons: `ж•°жҚ®еҲғ (Data Blade)`, `и„үеҶІжһӘ (Pulse Gun)`, `йҖ»иҫ‘зӮёеј№ (Logic Bomb)`

#### [NEW] [css/map.css](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/css/map.css)
- Grid-based map renderer, fog effect, tile styling
- Mobile-responsive tap targets

#### [NEW] [css/combat.css](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/css/combat.css)
- ATB bar, fighter display, shake/depress animations

