## Proposed Changes вҖ” Phase 5: Endgame

#### [NEW] [script/matrix_sink.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/matrix_sink.js)
- Unlocked after exploring enough of the map
- Player pours ember into the matrix. Progress: `0.0000%` вҶ’ `100.0000%`
- Scaling cost: each 0.0001% costs more ember than the last (logarithmic curve)
- At 100%: unlock coordinate (0,0) on the map

#### [NEW] [script/endgame.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/endgame.js)
- Enter (0,0) вҶ’ full-screen red flash, erosion +10/s
- Three philosophy questions displayed sequentially
- Player must drag/click the correct artifact (`жҗәеёҰжқӮйҹізҡ„еҝғи·ійў‘ж®ө`) from a pile of items before erosion hits 100
- Correct submission вҶ’ logic deadlock animation вҶ’ true ending sequence
- Wrong submission or timeout вҶ’ death ending вҶ’ recorded in gallery

#### [MODIFY] [ship.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/ship.js)
- Re-theme as `иЈӮйҡҷж–№иҲҹ (Rift Ark)` вҖ” a recovered vessel that can pierce into God Space
- Upgrade resources changed: `alien alloy` вҶ’ `зҒ°иҙЁ (Gray Matter)` + `дҪҺиҜӯеҖј (Whispers)`
- Hull/thruster upgrades вҶ’ `з»ҙеәҰжҠӨзӣҫ (Dimensional Shield)` / `иЈӮйҡҷеј•ж“Һ (Rift Engine)`
- Liftoff triggers entry into God Space (Space module) as an **alternate route** to (0,0)

#### [MODIFY] [space.js](file:///Users/quantumrose/Documents/Emberois/adarkroom/script/space.js)
- Re-theme as `зҘһеҹҹз©ҝи¶Ҡ (God Space Transit)` вҖ” asteroid field becomes `ж•°жҚ®зўҺзүҮжөҒ (Data Fragment Stream)`
- Ship dodges corruption fragments; hull damage = erosion increase
- Successful transit вҶ’ arrives at the same endgame FSM as (0,0) coordinate
- Crash вҶ’ death ending with unique narrative (different from map death)
- Retains keyboard controls and visual animation framework

